&lt;h1&gt;Orthopeadic Surgical Assistant&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are pleased to announce in Musculoskeletal Care Clinical Business Unit, exciting opportunities to join our progressive Orthopaedic Surgical Assistants team, working across two sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These are the Cheshire &amp; Merseyside Treatment Centre based on the Halton site and the Warrington site and the posts are permanent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic individuals with the experience to work autonomously by using the First Assistant qualification and deliver assistance to our Orthopaedic Surgeons in the theatre setting, adhering to the Trust values and behaviours.&lt;/p&gt;
